    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, representing the very best the used market has to offer. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint gleams with a deep, rich luster, free of scratches, chips, or blemishes, and all body panels align perfectly with no signs of prior damage or repair. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls, displays, and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, confident power, and all mechanical systems are in excellent working order with up-to-date maintenance. This is a turnkey vehicle for the discerning buyer who wants a used car that feels and performs like new.",
