    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "An absolutely stunning opportunity for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise! This vehicle is in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. From the gleaming exterior to the spotless, fresh-feeling interior, this car presents like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every system runs beautifully, the finish is flawless, and there's virtually no wear to speak of inside or out. If you've been searching for a truly exceptional, move-in-ready vehicle that you can be proud to drive every single day, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something genuinely special!",
