    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Solid Value & Ready to Roll \u2013 A Honest Fair-Condition Find! \ud83d\ude99\n\nLooking for a practical, drivable car without breaking the bank? This one is worth a look! We'll be upfront: this vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it has some visible wear and minor cosmetic imperfections that come with its age and use, but it runs and gets you where you need to go. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's a reliable everyday option for a budget-conscious buyer who appreciates honesty over hype. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint shines with a deep, rich luster, free of any scratches, dents, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim, glass, and chrome accents are all in pristine shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new: the upholstery shows no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is clean and unmarked. All controls, buttons, and features function exactly as intended, with no warning lights, rattles, or quirks of any kind. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, and the car drives with the smooth, responsive confidence of a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 just drive and enjoy.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a solid everyday driver without breaking the bank? This vehicle might be just what you need! It's in fair condition \u2014 meaning it runs and gets you where you need to go, but it does show its age with some wear and minor imperfections both inside and out. You may want to budget for some maintenance or cosmetic touch-ups down the road, but the bones are there for a reliable ride. A great option for a practical buyer who wants transportation value without the premium price tag!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about its state before you consider purchasing. The exterior has sustained considerable damage \u2014 expect deep scratches, multiple dents, and areas where rust has begun to develop. The paint is faded and peeling in several spots, giving the car a noticeably worn appearance. The interior is similarly rough: the upholstery is torn and stained, some trim pieces are cracked or missing, and the dashboard shows heavy wear. Mechanically, the car runs but requires attention \u2014 there are known issues that will need to be addressed, and we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. This vehicle is best suited for someone looking for a project car, parts, or a very budget-conscious buyer who is comfortable taking on repairs. We are pricing it accordingly and honestly to reflect its true condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
